,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T15:43:25.000Z","msg":"大型除咗島嶼同日本都有買<br />\n覺得get together最悶（雖然地圖好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我嫌煩唔多中意俾人仔gathering 所以好後悔買咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大學玩一次就正 但因為今次同之前幾代唔一樣<br />\n會用返人仔條命啲時間去讀書，啲課程又長時間又多task<br />\n次次大學畢業都變中年人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反而自己幾中意星夢<br />\n覺得拍戲/做kol 幾好玩<br />\n仲好玩過有三個新增職業嘅來去上班（黑警個職業仲要有bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都會有多啲event同apartment 都唔錯，中意佢個地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n動物同四季就睇下你有無興趣<br />\n有啲節日都幾得意<br />\n<br />\n綠色生活仲摸索緊，啲技能好難練<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過整體傢俬+新嘢都好似幾得意<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想搭單問下有無人買咗織嘢個個pack<br />\n想知多唔多嘢玩"},{"pid":"d9e32b484a78527acd767032a0308b2fdd2f245e","tid":2286721,"uid":15870,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"邊隻最好玩都有討論空間，抵唔抵就肯肯定全部都唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加個少少嘢就想收百幾二百，50蚊一隻就差唔多"},{"pid":"d2a900e430ca912a048ed87a2bcfa14075bb061f","tid":2286721,"uid":48080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9e32b484a78527acd767032a0308b2fdd2f245e","tid":2286721,"uid":15870,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"邊隻最好玩都有討論空間，抵唔抵就肯肯定全部都唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加個少少嘢就想收百幾二百，50蚊一隻就差唔多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:17:47.000Z","msg":"佢啲dlc我全部都係半價先買 但係計計埋埋都洗左過千<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nEA真係好撚識計數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff46e06f4f10b60e75fbefc4